  "Expeditions introduced pre-1.0 in patch v0.4.11 (Feybreak era, Jan 2025); hard-mode expeditions and firepower->quantity scaling added by v0.6.4.",
  "1.0 (update 1.100.427) extended expeditions into Sunreach and the World Tree and appears to have rebalanced VeryHard expeditions (pre-1.0 wiki listed them at 60 min / 500K firepower; 1.0 data shows 120 min / 1.6M).",
  "VeryHard expeditions each guarantee a specific raid-slab fragment (e.g. Eternal Pyre's Forbidden Market and PAL Genetic Research Laboratory -> Xenolord Slab Fragment) plus a Kinship Peach.",
  "World Tree expeditions are the expedition source of Ancient Relics and Radiant Gems (1.0 Awakening mechanic).",
  "2026-07-15: unlock corrected to paldb 1.0 (tech 22; Wooden Board 10, Stone 100, Paldium Fragment 20). palworld.wiki.gg had EA-era values (tech 15; Wood 20, Stone 20, Paldium 5)."
 ],
